      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. From its flawless exterior to its spotless interior, every detail has been meticulously preserved. If you're looking for a top-tier vehicle that represents the pinnacle of care and quality, this is the one for you!",
