      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and would best suit someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine requires significant attention, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping during gear changes. Externally, there is substantial body wear including rust patches and several dents, while the interior shows heavy staining and tears in the upholstery. Despite these issues, the car is still largely intact, offering potential for a buyer willing to invest the necessary time and repairs.",
